Lynn Cohen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lynn_Cohen 0 Lynn Cohen (born August 10, 1933) is an American actress. She is best known for playing Magda in the HBO series Sex and the City and the 2008 film of the same name, as well as its 2010 sequel, and Mags in The Hunger Games: Catching Fire.She has also played Judge Elizabeth Mizener several times on Law Order, and has appeared in the movies Munich, Vanya on 42nd Street, Synecdoche, New York, and Eagle Eye.
